# ================================
# TripMind - Monorepo Root
# ================================
# This project has 3 separate apps, each with their own .env file:
#
# apps/api/.env          → FastAPI backend secrets
# apps/web/.env.local    → Next.js web app secrets
# apps/mobile/.env       → Expo mobile app secrets
#
# Copy the .env.example in each folder to get started.
# NEVER commit any .env files to git!